comments: Horford (BOS) makes contact with Stephenson's (IND) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Tatum (BOS) legally contests the jump shot attempt by Brissett (IND).
Brown (BOS) initiates body contact with Brissett (IND) that affects his driving shot attempt.  After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of a common foul is confirmed.
Bitadze (IND) briefly places an arm around Horford's (BOS) opposite-side hip but quickly corrects.
White (BOS) bobbles the ball during his drive to the basket and maintains his pivot foot upon regaining possession.
Smart (BOS) legally contests Brissett's (IND) jump shot attempt by jumping to his side.
Washington Jr. (IND) absorbs the incidental contact created by White (BOS) during his driving shot attempt.
Tatum (BOS) legally contests the jump shot attempt by Brissett (IND).
